info.title: Information about UAEU Space
info.paragraph1: 1. UAEU Space is a multi-purpose platform for UAEU students to prepare them during their studies. You can find and share materials for courses that are taken by the university's students.
info.paragraph2: 2. Courses and professors data are collected from the University's official website.
